Description: A discrete event simulation package for modelling patient flow in a
    hospital emergency room. Patients arrive randomly, are triaged into priority
    categories, wait in a priority queue, and are served by configurable medical
    staff resources. Tracks key performance indicators including waiting time,
    queue length, patients served, and resource utilisation. Includes an
    interactive Shiny dashboard for configuring and visualising simulations.
